abstract: Commerce Dept revises fourth-quarter gross domestic product growth to 1.4 percent annually, from 1 percent.
lead_paragraph: Gross domestic product increased at a 1.4 percent annual rate, helped by stronger consumer spending.

headline.main: G.D.P. for 4th Quarter Is Revised Upward
headline.print_headline: 4th Quarter Looks Stronger After Figures Are Updated

snippet: Gross domestic product increased at a 1.4 percent annual rate, helped by stronger consumer spending.
